metadata.name: OG COWL #1/500
metadata.description: On 04/26/2022 one of the best community came to an existence on the NFT Tweeter after minting Original Cowls. All the OG COWL members of this community share same vibes and vision. This NFT has been created by ARK (The Masque) to give special homage and commemorate each and every single OG COWL member of the Community.
